- In Dart, any class can act as an interface. You implement an interface using the `implements` keyword. Example:

      ```dart
      class Dog implements Animal {
        @override
        void makeSound() {
          print('Bark');
        }

        @override
        void breathe() {
          print('Panting...');
        }
      }
      ```

